1. *Torbe* su poredane u ormaru. (Bags are arranged in the closet.)
2. Kupila sam nove *torbe* u prodavnici. (I bought new bags at the store.)
3. On je nosio teške *torbe* do stana. (He carried heavy bags to the apartment.)
4. *Torbe* koje nosiš su previše teške za mene. (The bags you are carrying are too heavy for me.)
5. Prodavačica je stavila moju kupovinu u *torbu*. (The saleswoman put my purchase in a bag.)
6. Ova *torba* je dovoljno velika da stane sve što mi je potrebno. (This bag is big enough to fit everything I need.)
7. Ispred tržnog centra je bilo puno ljudi sa velikim *torbama* u rukama. (There were many people with large bags in their hands in front of the shopping center.)
8. Moramo pronaći način da smanjimo količinu plastičnih *torbi* koje koristimo. (We need to find a way to reduce the amount of plastic bags we use.)